entries.content: The final three tracks have previously been labelled DE5932p,q,r. These recordings were subsequently discovered to have been from the previous session, and moved there as DE5932xd,xe,xf. New recordings of these three titles from this session have since emerged. They have not been assigned a New DESOR number. See [this article](https://ellington.se/2019/02/04/copenhagen-sep-30-1959-corrected/) from DESS and (issue #71)(https://github.com/ellingtonia/ellingtonia/issues/71)
